392
00:31:04,830 --> 00:31:05,870
I was careless.

393
00:31:06,750 --> 00:31:07,670
Don't worry, Madam.

394
00:31:08,430 --> 00:31:09,550
If anything happens, I'll take the fall.

395
00:31:09,590 --> 00:31:10,590
You'll take the fall?

396
00:31:10,670 --> 00:31:11,870
How?

397
00:31:12,310 --> 00:31:14,350
It's always me who has to cover for you.

398
00:31:15,350 --> 00:31:16,990
The police are definitely
watching you now.

399
00:31:17,030 --> 00:31:17,790
Lie low,

400
00:31:19,150 --> 00:31:20,750
and stay out of our business
in Halan for a while.

401
00:31:21,630 --> 00:31:22,630
Understood.

402
00:31:40,190 --> 00:31:41,870
Be extra careful

403
00:31:42,430 --> 00:31:44,190
with this new batch.

404
00:31:44,710 --> 00:31:45,830
Keep an eye out at all times.

405
00:31:45,830 --> 00:31:46,990
We can't afford any slip-ups.

406
00:31:46,990 --> 00:31:47,830
Got it?

407
00:31:48,510 --> 00:31:49,310
Yingzi?

408
00:32:09,230 --> 00:32:10,470
Why are you here so early today?

409
00:32:10,550 --> 00:32:11,830
There wasn't much going on
at the factory today,

410
00:32:11,830 --> 00:32:13,110
so I came over early.

411
00:32:24,230 --> 00:32:25,150
Happy birthday.

412
00:32:28,510 --> 00:32:29,870
We're already an old married couple.

413
00:32:29,870 --> 00:32:31,230
Why bother buying me flowers?

414
00:32:31,550 --> 00:32:32,510
What a waste of money.

415
00:32:33,590 --> 00:32:34,990
It didn't cost much.

416
00:32:34,990 --> 00:32:35,870
I saw them on my way here,

417
00:32:35,870 --> 00:32:37,190
so I just bought some.

418
00:32:37,550 --> 00:32:39,590
They were grown in a greenhouse.

419
00:32:39,910 --> 00:32:40,710
They've got such a bright color.

420
00:32:41,550 --> 00:32:42,910
I still have some accounts to go over.

421
00:32:42,910 --> 00:32:43,910
Why don't you rest for a bit?

422
00:32:43,990 --> 00:32:44,710
Sure.

423
00:32:44,710 --> 00:32:46,190
- Once I'm done, we'll head home.
- Okay.

424
00:32:46,910 --> 00:32:47,750
Don't overwork yourself.

425
00:33:02,510 --> 00:33:03,670
Did you bring your camera?

426
00:33:04,070 --> 00:33:04,870
Of course.

427
00:33:04,910 --> 00:33:06,910
How could I go to a concert
without a camera?

428
00:33:07,990 --> 00:33:09,590
Don't just take pictures of your idols.

429
00:33:09,710 --> 00:33:11,390
Get some shots of the scenery too.

430
00:33:12,110 --> 00:33:13,870
I haven't been to the capital yet.

431
00:33:15,070 --> 00:33:17,150
Take some pictures
of the Great Wall for me.

432
00:33:17,910 --> 00:33:19,110
I'm only there for two days.

433
