I won't have time

434
00:33:20,150 --> 00:33:21,670
to visit the Great Wall.

435
00:33:22,470 --> 00:33:23,070
Fine.

436
00:33:30,550 --> 00:33:31,350
Stop right there!

437
00:33:33,470 --> 00:33:34,270
Are you alright?

438
00:33:34,430 --> 00:33:35,470
Are you hurt?

439
00:33:35,990 --> 00:33:36,790
Ouch, my ankle.

440
00:33:39,150 --> 00:33:39,950
I twisted my ankle.

441
00:33:40,350 --> 00:33:41,390
It's my fault.

442
00:33:41,390 --> 00:33:42,510
I was careless.

443
00:33:42,590 --> 00:33:44,150
How is this your fault?

444
00:33:44,270 --> 00:33:45,790
That motorcycle guy was going too fast.

445
00:33:45,950 --> 00:33:46,790
It's his fault.

446
00:33:47,870 --> 00:33:49,470
You need to go home
and put some medicine on.

447
00:33:49,550 --> 00:33:51,910
I can't. I need to catch my train.

448
00:33:51,910 --> 00:33:53,310
- Let me help you. Be careful.
- Ouch.

449
00:34:00,150 --> 00:34:01,630
The bike's broken now.

450
00:34:01,990 --> 00:34:02,830
Let's get a cab.

451
00:34:03,990 --> 00:34:04,790
We'll get a cab.

452
00:34:05,550 --> 00:34:06,710
We're almost there.

453
00:34:06,710 --> 00:34:07,910
Taking a cab would be a waste of money.

454
00:34:07,910 --> 00:34:08,910
I'll just hop my way over.

455
00:34:09,430 --> 00:34:10,830
Don't be ridiculous.

456
00:34:12,870 --> 00:34:13,870
Once you're on the train,

457
00:34:14,590 --> 00:34:16,270
ask the attendant for some ice

458
00:34:16,870 --> 00:34:18,190
or an iced soda.

459
00:34:18,750 --> 00:34:20,470
Use it to ice your ankle.

460
00:34:21,190 --> 00:34:22,070
Alright.

461
00:34:22,070 --> 00:34:23,830
You're nagging at me like my brother.

462
00:34:24,230 --> 00:34:25,590
Look at you. You're sweating

463
00:34:26,470 --> 00:34:28,110
like you've just washed your face.

464
00:34:29,390 --> 00:34:30,950
You need to work out more often.

465
00:34:31,470 --> 00:34:32,670
That's because I'm a young man

466
00:34:32,670 --> 00:34:33,830
with a fast metabolism.

467
00:34:34,390 --> 00:34:36,710
You twisted your ankle,
and you're still making fun of me?

468
00:34:38,550 --> 00:34:42,110
Why are you walking so unevenly?

469
00:34:42,600 --> 00:34:44,560
Am I that heavy?

470
00:34:45,120 --> 00:34:46,280
You're as light

471
00:34:46,640 --> 00:34:47,760
as a feather.

472
00:34:48,840 --> 00:34:50,640
Then what's going on with you?

473
00:34:51,160 --> 00:34:52,840
Worry about yourself first.

474
00:34:54,440 --> 00:34:57,560
Do you know
the medical term for a twisted ankle?

475
00:34:58,320 --> 00:34:59,760
It's called an ankle sprain.

476
00:35:00,200 --> 00:35:01,480
You should take it seriously.

477
00:35:02,120 --> 00:35:05,000
Ice your ankle tonight,

478
00:35:05,120 --> 00:35:06,880
and apply heat to it tomorrow night.

479
00:35:13,720 --> 00:35:15,080
Stop shaking your head.

480
00:35:15,320 --> 00:35:16,440
Are you listening to me?

481
00:35:18,920 --> 00:35:20,640
The hotel room has a kettle, right?

482
00:35:22,480 --> 00:35:23,560
Boil some water,

483
00:35:24,160 --> 00:35:25,760
heat up a towel,

484
00:35:26,360 --> 00:35:27,960
wrap it in a plastic bag,
and put it on your ankle.

485
00:35:28,880 --> 00:35:30,400
It'll help reduce bruising.

486
00:35:32,280 --> 00:35:33,200
It's partly my fault.

487
00:35:34,200 --> 00:35:37,080
With the train station so close,

488
00:35:37,880 --> 00:35:39,960
I thought it was unnecessary
to drive you there in Bei's car.

489
00:35:44,760 --> 00:35:46,240
That car's low on gas anyway.

490
00:35:47,040 --> 00:35:48,720
We would've had to
detour to the gas station.

491
00:35:49,600 --> 00:35:51,760
That could've
made you miss your train...

492
00:35:56,200 --> 00:35:57,200
What's wrong?

493
00:35:58,920 --> 00:36:00,360
Let's go to the hospital.

494
00:36:04,080 --> 00:36:05,320
Why?

495
00:36:05,760 --> 00:36:07,280
This is just a scrape.

496
00:36:09,000 --> 00:36:10,680
We're almost at the station.

497
00:36:11,040 --> 00:36:12,920
You still have that concert to go to.

498
00:36:15,880 --> 00:36:16,880
Stop moving! Don't...

499
00:36:16,960 --> 00:36:18,240
Be careful

500
