with your ankle.

501
00:36:19,200 --> 00:36:20,280
I'm not going!

502
00:36:21,360 --> 00:36:22,240
Let's go to the hospital.

503
00:36:27,440 --> 00:36:29,360
Time for cake!

504
00:36:35,840 --> 00:36:36,600
It's so sweet!

505
00:36:36,600 --> 00:36:38,640
I love cream cakes!

506
00:36:38,720 --> 00:36:40,040
I'll buy you

507
00:36:40,040 --> 00:36:42,160
an even bigger one
for your birthday, okay?

508
00:36:42,240 --> 00:36:43,040
Okay!

509
00:36:44,360 --> 00:36:45,360
Jianmin.

510
00:36:49,230 --> 00:36:52,830
♪Happy birthday to you♪

511
00:36:53,150 --> 00:36:56,430
♪Happy birthday to you♪

512
00:36:56,630 --> 00:36:59,870
♪Happy birthday to you♪

513
00:37:00,150 --> 00:37:06,630
♪Happy birthday to you♪

514
00:37:07,030 --> 00:37:08,230
Thank you!

515
00:37:08,230 --> 00:37:09,030
Wait.

516
00:37:09,110 --> 00:37:10,070
Make a wish first.

517
00:37:10,310 --> 00:37:10,790
Right.

518
00:37:10,790 --> 00:37:11,750
Make a wish.

519
00:37:11,910 --> 00:37:15,310
I hope Mommy makes
lots and lots of money

520
00:37:15,470 --> 00:37:17,430
so she can buy me lots of presents!

521
00:37:17,550 --> 00:37:18,390
You little smart cookie,

522
00:37:18,390 --> 00:37:19,750
always getting the first wish
on everyone's birthday.

523
00:37:19,750 --> 00:37:20,790
Let your mommy go first.

524
00:37:21,870 --> 00:37:23,990
Actually, my wish is very simple.

525
00:37:24,710 --> 00:37:26,390
I just hope everyone in our family

526
00:37:26,790 --> 00:37:29,070
can stay safe and happy.

527
00:37:29,750 --> 00:37:31,030
Make the wish in your heart.

528
00:37:31,110 --> 00:37:32,910
If you say it out loud,
it won't come true.

529
00:37:33,110 --> 00:37:34,430
- Alright.
- Make another wish.

530
00:37:40,510 --> 00:37:41,230
Done.

531
00:37:41,790 --> 00:37:42,670
Let's blow out the candles.

532
00:37:42,910 --> 00:37:44,790
One, two, three.

533
00:37:48,590 --> 00:37:49,750
Let's cut the cake!

534
00:37:49,750 --> 00:37:51,950
Time to cut the cake!

535
00:37:52,550 --> 00:37:54,350
Let's give the first piece
to Daddy, okay?

536
00:37:54,950 --> 00:37:55,790
Give it to Mao first.

537
00:37:55,790 --> 00:37:56,470
Here, Mao.

538
00:37:56,790 --> 00:37:57,550
Give her this one,

539
00:37:57,710 --> 00:37:58,710
