540
00:37:58,710 --> 00:37:59,350
That one? Okay.

541
00:37:59,350 --> 00:38:00,470
Here you go, Mao.

542
00:38:00,910 --> 00:38:02,550
Now, let's give your uncle a big piece.

543
00:38:04,110 --> 00:38:05,470
Look how skinny you are.

544
00:38:05,510 --> 00:38:06,590
Eat more.

545
00:38:09,350 --> 00:38:10,350
Yingzi,

546
00:38:11,550 --> 00:38:13,110
thank you for giving me

547
00:38:14,310 --> 00:38:15,190
