549
00:38:19,830 --> 00:38:21,510
Thank you for being
so understanding of us.

550
00:38:23,510 --> 00:38:24,670
I'm so glad

551
00:38:26,630 --> 00:38:27,710
I didn't miss out on you.

552
00:38:36,270 --> 00:38:37,830
In order to win Mommy's heart,

553
00:38:37,830 --> 00:38:39,390
