554
00:38:40,510 --> 00:38:41,870
What should you call him?

555
00:38:42,070 --> 00:38:43,350
It's Mommy's birthday today,

556
00:38:43,350 --> 00:38:45,190
so Mao is especially happy, right?

557
00:38:45,310 --> 00:38:48,110
Here, this piece of chocolate
is for you.

558
00:38:48,110 --> 00:38:49,310
Do you like it?

559
00:38:50,350 --> 00:38:51,230
You little smart cookie,

560
00:38:51,230 --> 00:38:52,710
you really do know everything.

561
00:38:54,750 --> 00:38:58,070
Whenever Mommy and I go to the park,
he's always there.

562
00:38:58,330 --> 00:39:03,650
