563
00:39:10,630 --> 00:39:12,430
Are you fishing?

564
00:39:14,710 --> 00:39:15,510
Yes.

565
00:39:16,710 --> 00:39:17,750
Keep your voice down.

566
00:39:21,550 --> 00:39:23,990
But where are the fish?

567
00:39:28,030 --> 00:39:30,750
The fish are in the water.

